'''House Harbright''' was a wealthy family influential in the [[Salliche Agricultural Corporation|Salliche Ag Corporation]]. In [[25 ABY/Legends|25 ABY]] its leader was [[Count/Legends|Count]] [[Borert Harbright]]. Other members were Lady [[Selnia Harbright]] and [[Dees Harbright]]. The family had served the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] for three centuries.<ref name="The Void Terror">{{JournalCite|3|The Void Terror}}</ref>

